Subject: [PATCH] Add Thymeleaf web UI (Projektaufgabe 2): mall,floor,shop,customer

Add a Thymeleaf view layer: MallService, view controllers for mall/floor/shop/customer,
register MallService bean in AppConfig, and add Thymeleaf templates (index + form)
for mall, floor, shop, customer.

This complements the existing REST API by adding the HTML UI required by the assignment.
